==Enemies==
{{Main|Soul Blazer:Enemies}}

Soul Blazer features over 50 enemy types across 6 acts, spawning from Soul Lairs.

==Bosses==
{{Main|Soul Blazer:Bosses}}

8 major boss battles guard each act:
* '''Metal Mantis''' (Act 1) - HP: 100, weak to Fire
* '''Plantentacle''' (Act 2) - HP: 150, weak to Fire magic
* '''Poseidon''' (Act 3) - HP: 200, weak to Thunder
* '''Stone Guardian''' (Act 4) - HP: 180, weak to Magic Flare
* '''Tin Doll''' (Act 5) - HP: 250, weak to Spark Bomb
* '''Ghost Ship Captain''' (Act 5) - HP: 200, requires Spirit Sword
* '''Demon Bird''' (Act 6) - HP: 300, weak to Tornado
* '''Deathtoll''' (Final) - HP: 900 total (3 phases)

